weights_tier1: VTI, TLT, GLD, DBC, VGK, VWO, HYG
weights_tier2: VTI, TLT, GLD, DBC, VGK, VWO
weights_tier3: VTI, TLT, GLD, DBC

Use tier1 if you can handle the transaction costs of more assets.

Use tier 2 if you can handle the transaction costs of more assets, but don't want to include corporate debt.

Use tier 3 if you can't handle transaction costs of too many assets.